@badger41 wrote:

remove all the animationconfigs out of class20.java and see if you still get the unpacking error.

if you do, there is an animation config in there that cant/wont load because of it being corrupted, too big for the client to buffer, or theres an error in the config, (ex, one of the frames in the config being 1 23 with no comma or not being 1 number)
